**Request**: Uncomment the `os.RemoveAll(f.build.tempDir)` logic and its associated error handling inside `cleanTemp()`.
**Why**: Leaving this cleanup code commented out causes a temporary directory leak on the user's filesystem every time they deploy.

## Comment 3 — Unfinished CLI documentation
**Severity**: approve-blocker
